{"tid":884184,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分左手一個半月 我前仔開過百個假ac滋擾我","createTime":"2018-10-31T11:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T13:26:49.000Z","uid":131299,"like":1,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"36b489237abc489ee9080f68a5f9f5f3a21b1363","tid":884184,"uid":131299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/192058_b3b8fa003797388dd09af431a3ebb1a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F192058_b3b8fa003797388dd09af431a3ebb1a3.png&h=4e6a3807&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/192101_da79afdc5b2c204c7e99126887f19e9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F192101_da79afdc5b2c204c7e99126887f19e9d.png&h=9c5088e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n既然你比得你嘅連登帳號我 <br />\n我亦都唔會姑辜你嘅好意<br />\n我同ex係ig交友網站識 <br />\n當時嘅我只係諗住拍散拖就算 <br />\n無諗到會識到個痴線佬 <br />\n係Long D 嘅時候 佢嘅本性仲未暴露 <br />\n翻到香港就仆街了 <br />\n我出街著短褲會被佢罵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我出街望左個男仔一眼 會被佢罵到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我Ig睇靚仔 佢會話我意圖出軌 唔愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話同朋友去op玩 <br />\n佢覺得我會同異性有親密接觸 話唔好去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最痴線嘅嚟喇 <br />\n佢話我翻學係男女校 有好多男仔 會有親密接觸 話比我五百蚊一日唔好翻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分左手之後 佢嚟我學校門口等我 不停同我朋友講 我真係好愛佢 我唔信有其他人會對佢比我更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲打擾我屋企人 同我老母講 我真係好愛你個囡<br />\n最仆街嘅係 佢幾乎次次都date我上佢屋企 <br />\n我讀緊中五咋大佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a55756d952e82fd0af0d7c1bfa5906055f046f5","tid":884184,"uid":201604,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"想知點搵到中五女仔拍拖"},{"pid":"76cb21f66f63a8839e6fce3a8114c8e8b8b2a96a","tid":884184,"uid":115775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"你ＥＸ幾歲？"},{"pid":"b4333b3c867945dcefd36938ac4a676845152a75","tid":884184,"uid":68851,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"死臭雞 上網識"},{"pid":"b15454fb1a924f38186437547a1144a064543143","tid":884184,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4333b3c867945dcefd36938ac4a676845152a75","tid":884184,"uid":68851,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"死臭雞 上網識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"交友網"},{"pid":"28ae72f22b7b62a11c62058ea03c94898cfe07fc","tid":884184,"uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"報警啦<br />\n騷擾黎，法庭出禁令 禁佢老味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8685f0b94c0d2c4c636ab28b5d08b91cd834e57e","tid":884184,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主專心讀書把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4890e7190e40f373a18abcb5f6bf24831055640f","tid":884184,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴到咁 <br />\n絲打出入小心d好"},{"pid":"d9f9b4c6be540e4c3a73424b238c3155ad9383fb","tid":884184,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"扑左野未"},{"pid":"8279fe1c5a167ac29df582f9e9bc08eafe05bb7d","tid":884184,"uid":131299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a55756d952e82fd0af0d7c1bfa5906055f046f5","tid":884184,"uid":201604,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"re